{
  "id": "69d39bbb06d5cda47b8c88c9",
  "title": "Miiの引き継ぎ方法",
  "created": 1775475645,
  "updated": 1775478501,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d39bbb06d5cda47b8c88c9",
      "text": "Miiの引き継ぎ方法",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475645,
      "updated": 1775475645
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bbc000000000093acc3",
      "text": ">[https://x.com/eku8reza/status/2040420304267489630?s=20 @eku8reza]:",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475645,
      "updated": 1775475649
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bc1000000000093acc7",
      "text": ">[トモダチコレクション わくわく生活]に今までの[Mii]を持っていきたい人へ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475649,
      "updated": 1775475663
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bbe000000000093acc4",
      "text": ">様々な場所からのMiiの搬送経路です。参考にしてください",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475646,
      "updated": 1775475646
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bbe000000000093acc5",
      "text": ">[https://gyazo.com/443034fe96ea886715176532476afd72]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475646,
      "updated": 1775475672
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bbe000000000093acc6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475646,
      "updated": 1775475646
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bd9000000000093acc9",
      "text": "補足",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475674,
      "updated": 1775476160
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39c3a000000000093accb",
      "text": "\tほとんどの経路で[3DS]の[Miiスタジオ]が必要になる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475771,
      "updated": 1775475953
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39cf4000000000093accd",
      "text": "\t\t引っ越ししたWiiとWii Uは独自の経路があるが、DSと3DSと未引っ越しのWiiはMiiスタジオを介さないといけない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475957,
      "updated": 1775476067
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a5c8000000000093acd3",
      "text": "\t\t[トモダチコレクション 新生活 Mii引っ越しソフト]は新規ダウンロードはできない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775478216,
      "updated": 1775478447
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a6af000000000093acd4",
      "text": "\t\t\t再ダウンロードは可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775478447,
      "updated": 1775478451
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3a6b2000000000093acd5",
      "text": "\t\t\tなので、新規ユーザーが[DS]版[トモダチコレクション]からMiiを移動する時は、[Miiスタジオ]を介すのが良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775478451,
      "updated": 1775478501
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39d0d000000000093acce",
      "text": "\t更に現状では[amiibo]も必須になる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475982,
      "updated": 1775475999
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39d9f000000000093accf",
      "text": "\t\t1個のamiiboにつき1つまでしか入れられない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775476128,
      "updated": 1775476167
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39db7000000000093acd0",
      "text": "\t\t\t[任天堂の『amiibo』なんですけれど、アレって『mii』も入れられるのは分か... - Yahoo!知恵袋 https://detail.chiebukuro.yahoo.co.jp/qa/question_detail/q14274797369]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775476152,
      "updated": 1775476152
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39dc8000000000093acd2",
      "text": "\t\t複数体を効率良く移行するには複数個のamiiboがあると良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775476168,
      "updated": 1775476168
    },
    {
      "id": "69d39bda000000000093acca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775475674,
      "updated": 1775475674
    }
  ]
}